## Project Structure

```
1.Prompt_Image/
├── main.py                     # Entry point + main window
├── config.json                 # App settings (output, threads, etc.)
├── api_keys.json               # API keys riêng biệt
├── requirements.txt
├── styles/                     # Style preset files
│   ├── Cinematic.txt
│   └── Documentary.txt
├── core/                       # Core logic
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── srt_parser.py           # Parse & group SRT segments
│   ├── api_client.py           # Multi-endpoint API + fallback
│   ├── prompt_generator.py     # Generate prompts from SRT
│   └── process_controller.py   # Start/Pause/Stop threading
└── ui/                         # UI components
    ├── __init__.py
    ├── main_window.py           # Main dashboard layout
    ├── settings_dialog.py       # Settings popup (API, Theme, Deps)
    ├── config_section.py        # Configuration section (Style, Mode, etc.)
    ├── projects_section.py      # Projects table + SRT actions
    ├── srt_preview.py           # SRT Preview panel
    ├── actions_section.py       # Action buttons (Process, Stop, etc.)
    └── log_section.py           # Processing log + status bar
```

